<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal David vang khawpi tuolnuom a chun,
 Sunni muolliem kuonin;
 Singkhuol nungak thiengtho liengthei Mari.
 Gieh na'ng mun a chang puoi'
 Bawng In sung a bel hi

[V2]
 2. Ngaitie zie mun tawm leh thawmhau a chun,
 Zan khuo a hung sawtin;
 Enna lopi tak chu a hung tungtai,
 Bethlehem bawng In ah,
 Lal thak a hung pieng tai.

[V3]
 3. A tel chuom puoi Lal In leh mun lopi.
 Mun niem a tel zaw ie!
 A mak na e! zie Lal deihum pen chu,
 A hehpih lei mite'n,
 Amah a deih puou ie,

[V4]
 4. Hehpihna chu a hung kilak ma chun,
 Pa kawma um a hi;
 Tanpa Pathien mihiem a hung chan hi,
 Ka tha'n a het phetin,
 Lunggil in mak asai

[V5]
 5. Aw Lalpa Isu, Nang hung kilak in,
 Ka lunggil sung ahin;
 Hetna thagui lunggil hi tuomvel in,
 Ei umpih zing inla,
 Kumsawt, kumsawt chanin</lyrics>
<title>Tawm Mahleh Lal A Hi</title>
<hymn_number>25</hymn_number>
</song>